@startuml
title 全渠道订单接入流程（以天猫 Webhook 为例）

actor "天猫" as tmall
participant "Channel Gateway" as cgw
participant "channel-adapter" as adapter
database "Redis" as redis
database "channel_raw_order" as rawdb
database "order" as ob
participant "order-core" as order
participant "workflow-service" as wf
queue "RocketMQ" as mq

== 订单推送 + 认证 ==

tmall -> cgw: POST /channel/tmall/webhook/order\n(签名 + 订单数据)
activate cgw

cgw -> cgw: 渠道认证 Filter
note right
  根据 X-Shop-Id 获取渠道店铺
  的 AppKey + Secret，验签
  支持 HMAC-SHA256 / OAuth2
end note

cgw -> redis: 渠道限流检查\n(Redis Lua 原子计数)
redis --> cgw: 允许

cgw -> adapter: 转发标准化后的原始请求
deactivate cgw

== 标准化处理 ==

activate adapter

adapter -> adapter: 1. 字段映射\n  天猫字段 → 中台标准字段
adapter -> redis: 2. 幂等检查\n  (channel_type + channel_order_no)

alt 已处理的订单
    redis --> adapter: 已存在
    adapter --> tmall: HTTP 200 (已处理，忽略)
    deactivate adapter
else 新订单

    adapter -> product_center: 3. 补全商品信息\n  (skuId → productId + category)
    product_center --> adapter: 商品信息

    adapter -> adapter: 4. 规则校验\n  必填字段 / 金额一致性

    adapter -> rawdb: 5. 保存原始订单\n  (channel_raw_order)
    rawdb --> adapter: 成功

    adapter -> order: 6. 创建标准化订单\n  (channel_type 已赋值)
    activate order

    note right of order
      此时的订单已包含
      channel_type= tmall
      channel_order_no= 渠道订单号
      channel_shop_id= 店铺标识
    end note

    order -> order: 状态机 INIT → PENDING_PAY
    order --> adapter: 创建成功 (order_no)
    deactivate order

    adapter -> mq: 发布 ChannelOrderReceivedEvent
    deactivate adapter

    == 走已有 Saga 流程 ==
    mq -> wf: 触发下单流程 (非必须, 异步)
    activate wf
    wf -> order: 启动 Saga 编排

    == 异步回写渠道 ==
    order -> mq: 订单状态变更事件 (交付/发货等)
    mq -> adapter: ChannelStatusSyncConsumer
    activate adapter
    adapter -> tmall: 回写订单状态 (syncStatus)
    tmall --> adapter: 成功
    adapter -> adapter: 记录同步日志
    deactivate adapter

    tmall --> cgw: HTTP 200 (处理成功)
    cgw --> tmall: HTTP 202 (已接受)
end

@enduml
